# Add Udev permition

## add you USER in the group of plugdev : 

sudo adduser USER plugdev

## add udev rules to detect USB lines

Add/edit the file : /etc/udev/rules.d/42-cycloide.rules
and add the following lines :

ATTRS{idVendor}=="F123", ATTRS{idProduct}=="4567", SUBSYSTEMS=="usb",           
ACTION=="add", MODE="0666", GROUP="plugdev"

Now reboot the computer
